      xml:id="resources.information.technologies.java.j2ee.ejb.ejb3.enterpriseBeans.sessionBeans.interception.interceptors.introParagraph">
  Interceptors enable one to intercept any of the business services offered by session and
  message-driven beans. They provide a mechanism for pluggable add-on responsibilities
  around business services. They may be used for filtering, custom security solutions, validation,
  or any other responsibility in the spirit of aspect-oriented programming.
</para>